==Slovak==
===Etymology===
:Derived from '''[[dobro#Slovak|dobro]]''', a noun meaning ''[[good]]''.
===Adverb===
:'''dobre'''
# [[well]]
# [[good]]
# [[thank goodness]]
===Examples===
* '''Maj sa dobre!''' &ndash; ''Be well!''
* '''Ako sa máš? Ďakujem, dobre.''' &ndash; ''How are you? Good, thanks.''
* '''Dobre, že neprší!''' &ndash; ''Thank goodness, it's not raining.''